graph TB
    subgraph "ODH Dashboard Pod"
        Frontend[Frontend<br/>React 18 + TypeScript SPA<br/>PatternFly 6]
        Backend[Backend<br/>Node.js/Fastify API Server<br/>Port 8080/TCP]
        RBACProxy[kube-rbac-proxy<br/>OAuth + TLS<br/>Port 8443/TCP]

        Frontend -->|serves| Backend
        RBACProxy -->|proxies to| Backend
    end

    subgraph "Modular Architecture (Optional)"
        ModelRegistryUI[model-registry-ui<br/>Micro-frontend<br/>Port 8043/TCP]
        GenAIUI[gen-ai-ui<br/>Micro-frontend<br/>Port 8143/TCP]
        MaaSUI[maas-ui<br/>Micro-frontend<br/>Port 8243/TCP]
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources Managed"
        OdhApplication[OdhApplication<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
        OdhDashboardConfig[OdhDashboardConfig<br/>opendatahub.io/v1alpha]
        OdhDocument[OdhDocument<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
        OdhQuickStart[OdhQuickStart<br/>console.openshift.io/v1]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    subgraph "Internal ODH Components"
        ODHOperator[ODH/RHODS Operator<br/>DataScienceCluster]
        Notebooks[Kubeflow Notebooks<br/>Notebook CRD]
        KServe[KServe<br/>InferenceService]
        ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>ModelRegistry CRD]
        Feast[Feast<br/>FeatureStore CRD]
    end

    User[User Browser] -->|HTTPS/8443<br/>OAuth Bearer| RBACProxy
    RBACProxy -->|OAuth flow| OAuthServer
    RBACProxy -->|HTTP/8080<br/>Impersonation| Backend

    Backend -->|manages| OdhApplication
    Backend -->|manages| OdhDashboardConfig
    Backend -->|manages| OdhDocument
    Backend -->|manages| OdhQuickStart

    Backend -->|HTTPS/443<br/>ServiceAccount Token| K8sAPI
    Backend -->|HTTPS/9091<br/>ServiceAccount Token| Prometheus

    Backend -->|watches| ODHOperator
    Backend -->|creates/manages| Notebooks
    Backend -->|watches| KServe
    Backend -->|manages| ModelRegistry
    Backend -->|watches| Feast

    Backend -->|module federation| ModelRegistryUI
    Backend -->|module federation| GenAIUI
    Backend -->|module federation| MaaSUI

